算在「總金額」上？","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"H10Ldj4SKovkvKxIlhxjz48tp2f"},{"block_id":"doxjp8ZnDcIBiwc1kmMrcsRvpNh","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1392,"token":"YjgBbBHbRogf1fxjkkxjHQZRp5b","width":1846},"parent_id":"H10Ldj4SKovkvKxIlhxjz48tp2f"},{"block_id":"doxjpPp2UhFd6FPRut7CS8hXnye","block_type":2,"parent_id":"H10Ldj4SKovkvKxIlhxjz48tp2f","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"答：「總金額」是有計算「在途現金」，「在途現金」有計算正在申購新股的資金，能更實際反映客戶資產；而客戶實際能使用的是「總可用現金」，是沒有加上這筆申購新股的資金。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}}]}